om/us/en/us-corporate-pay\n\nMicrosoft will accept applications for the role until September 15, 2025.\nResponsibilities\nPartner Cross-Functionally: Coordinate between Customer Growth Managers, Analytics, Data Science, Operations and Product Marketing on prioritization of cross-sell campaigns, targeting and metrics of success\nDrive customer usage by aligning marketing signals with sales engagement priorities: Leverage marketing insights to help sales teams identify and prioritize high-potential accounts, enabling timely and targeted outreach. Collaborate closely with sales to activate marketing-led engagement strategies that deepen customer relationships and accelerate product adoption.\nAgility & Influence: Demonstrates the ability to seamlessly shift across multiple priorities and requests, while effectively influencing stakeholders to adapt execution strategies based on the nature and urgency of each initiative.\nCommunicate Insights & Impact: Distill analyses of expansion campaigns into clear, actionable recommendations for senior leadership\nDrive Continuous Optimization: Establish feedback loops with stakeholders, set up process for planning and reporting\nAI-Driven Innovation: Leverage AI to enhance production, delivery and optimization of expansion campaigns—unlocking smarter targeting, faster execution, and deeper insights at scale.\nExperimentation mindset: Set up processes for experimentation and work closely with data science to identify opportunities of growth\nOther: Embody our Culture and Values",
